<br>
Basically, it's about what happens when some very powerful people start to use the net, in the futre (the net is virtual reality now) for some very very scary purposes, but there is SO much too it I can't even explain. VERY intricate plot, always keeps you hooked, VERY interesting and well-rounded characters, even the "villains". And he writes well. These books are a find.<br>
<br>
Also, if you liked Ender's Game there are 4 more books that come after it. I am currently reading the 2nd one, Speaker for the Dead, and it is very good. Almost done :) <p><center><b>Miyyu Kamatari</b></center>
